{"data":{"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Intellectyx, Inc","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/89093/intellectyx.png","srcSet":"/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/a15a6/intellectyx.png 175w,\n/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/8e4a7/intellectyx.png 350w,\n/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/89093/intellectyx.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/96e31/intellectyx.avif 175w,\n/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/c7b75/intellectyx.avif 350w,\n/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/f5f15/intellectyx.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/37045/intellectyx.webp 175w,\n/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/589aa/intellectyx.webp 350w,\n/static/90e61679c318389c988fe7dceeddf395/3216f/intellectyx.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":368}}},"tech":["FastAPI","OpenAI","Hugging Face","Pinecone","FAISS"],"github":null,"external":"https://www.intellectyx.com/","cta":null},"html":"<p>At Intellectyx, I built an LLM-powered knowledge assistant from 0 to 1 for enterprise document intelligence.\nThe product combined semantic search, document Q&#x26;A, and workflow automation using a full RAG pipeline from chunking and embeddings to retrieval and generation.\nI designed ingestion and data workflows for messy, unstructured content, then shipped low-latency FastAPI services with streaming responses for production usage.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Suki AI","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/65ff8/suki.jpg","srcSet":"/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/81770/suki.jpg 175w,\n/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/0b3a5/suki.jpg 350w,\n/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/65ff8/suki.jpg 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/96e31/suki.avif 175w,\n/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/c7b75/suki.avif 350w,\n/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/f5f15/suki.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/37045/suki.webp 175w,\n/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/589aa/suki.webp 350w,\n/static/0c31b3f829e891f28125670f10c6c4ba/3216f/suki.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":368}}},"tech":["LLMs","RAG","Speech-to-Text","NLP","Healthcare AI"],"github":"","external":"https://www.suki.ai/","cta":null},"html":"<p>At Suki AI, I contributed to an AI-powered clinical assistant used to streamline provider documentation and care workflows.\nI worked on LLM pipelines for note generation, summarization, and entity extraction, and helped integrate speech-to-text with downstream NLP processing.\nI also supported context-aware retrieval systems grounded in EHR and medical knowledge while maintaining healthcare-grade quality and compliance expectations.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Valvoline","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/89093/valvoline.png","srcSet":"/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/a15a6/valvoline.png 175w,\n/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/8e4a7/valvoline.png 350w,\n/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/89093/valvoline.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/96e31/valvoline.avif 175w,\n/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/c7b75/valvoline.avif 350w,\n/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/f5f15/valvoline.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/37045/valvoline.webp 175w,\n/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/589aa/valvoline.webp 350w,\n/static/bcca49d186dbe34188b7bc9ba88fb9d5/3216f/valvoline.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":368}}},"tech":["Java","Python","API Design","Data Pipelines"],"github":null,"external":"https://www.valvoline.com/","cta":"https://www.valvoline.com/"},"html":"<p>At Valvoline, I built features for a vehicle-based product recommendation and service platform used for maintenance and product selection workflows.\nI developed backend services in Java and Python for compatibility logic, product lookup, and recommendation experiences across a broad automotive catalog.\nI also helped automate ingestion and validation of vehicle and product datasets, improving reliability for customer-facing and service-facing applications.</p>"}}]}}}